# Fold marker **{

snippet fold "Fold marker block" b
`!p cms, fmr1, fmr2 = fold_marker()
snip.rv = cms` ${1:Description} `!p snip.rv = fmr1`

${2:${VISUAL}}

`!p snip.rv = cms + " " + fmr2`$0
endsnippet

